trans-unit.source: Specifies the padding mode and parameters to use with RSA encryption or decryption operations.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o modo de preenchimento e os parâmetros a serem usados com operações de criptografia ou descriptografia RSA.

trans-unit.source: The hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: O algoritmo hash.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> instance whose <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode" /> is <see cref="F:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPaddingMode.Oaep" /> with the given hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> cujo <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode" /> é <see cref="F:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPaddingMode.Oaep" /> com o algoritmo de hash fornecido.

trans-unit.source: An object whose mode is <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode" /> is <see cref="F:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPaddingMode.Oaep" /> with the hash algorithm specified by <paramref name="hashAlgorithm" />.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto cujo modo é <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode" /> é <see cref="F:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPaddingMode.Oaep" /> com o algoritmo de hash especificado pelo <paramref name="hashAlgorithm" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithmName.Name" /> property of <paramref name="hashAlgorithm" /> is either <see langword="null" /> or <see cref="F:System.String.Empty" />.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithmName.Name" /> de <paramref name="hashAlgorithm" /> é <see langword="null" /> ou <see cref="F:System.String.Empty" />.

trans-unit.source: Compares two <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> objects for equality.
trans-unit.target: Compara dois objetos <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> quanto à igualdade.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare.
trans-unit.target: O objeto a ser comparado.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the current instance is equal to the specified object.
trans-unit.target: Determina se a instância atual é igual ao objeto especificado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="obj" /> is equal to the current instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="obj" /> for igual a essa instância atual, caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: `obj` is equal to the current instance if it is a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding> object and the two objects have identical <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode%2A> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.OaepHashAlgorithm%2A> property values.
trans-unit.target: `obj` é igual à instância atual, se ele for um <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding> objeto e os dois objetos têm <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode%2A> e <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.OaepHashAlgorithm%2A> valores de propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare.
trans-unit.target: O objeto a ser comparado.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the current instance is equal to the specified <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Determina se a instância atual é igual ao objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="other" /> is equal to the current instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="other" /> for igual a essa instância atual, caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: `instance` and the current instance are equal if they have identical <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode%2A> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.OaepHashAlgorithm%2A> property values.
trans-unit.target: `instance` e a instância atual são iguais se eles tiverem idênticos <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode%2A> e <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.OaepHashAlgorithm%2A> valores de propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code of this <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o código hash deste objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" />.

trans-unit.source: The hash code of this instance.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o código hash dessa instância.

trans-unit.source: Gets the padding mode represented by this <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o modo de preenchimento representado por esta instância <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" />.

trans-unit.source: A padding mode.
trans-unit.target: Um modo de preenchimento.

trans-unit.source: Gets the hash algorithm used in conjunction with the <see cref="F:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPaddingMode.Oaep" /> padding mode.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o algoritmo de hash usado em conjunto com o modo de preenchimento <see cref="F:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPaddingMode.Oaep" />.

trans-unit.source: If the value of the <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode" /> property is not <see cref="F:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPaddingMode.Oaep" />, <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithmName.Name" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: O valor da propriedade de <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode" /> não é <see cref="F:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPaddingMode.Oaep" />, <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithmName.Name" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: O algoritmo hash.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that represents the Optimal Asymmetric Encryption Padding (OAEP) encryption standard with a SHA1 hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto que representa o padrão de criptografia OAEP (Preenchimento de Criptografia Assimétrica Ideal) com um algoritmo hash SHA1.

trans-unit.source: An object that represents the OAEP encryption standard with a SHA1 hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto que representa o padrão de criptografia OAEP com um algoritmo hash SHA1.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that represents the Optimal Asymmetric Encryption Padding (OAEP) encryption standard with a SHA256 hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto que representa o padrão de criptografia OAEP (Preenchimento de Criptografia Assimétrica Ideal) com um algoritmo hash SHA256.

trans-unit.source: An object that represents the OAEP encryption standard with a SHA256 hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto que representa o padrão de criptografia OAEP com um algoritmo de hash SHA256.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that represents the Optimal Asymmetric Encryption Padding (OAEP) encryption standard with a SHA-384 hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto que representa o padrão de criptografia OAEP (Preenchimento de Criptografia Assimétrica Ideal) com um algoritmo hash SHA-384.

trans-unit.source: An object that represents the OAEP encryption standard with a SHA384 hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto que representa o padrão de criptografia OAEP com um algoritmo de hash SHA384.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that represents the Optimal Asymmetric Encryption Padding (OAEP) encryption standard with a SHA512 hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto que representa o padrão de criptografia OAEP (Preenchimento de Criptografia Assimétrica Ideal) com um algoritmo hash SHA512.

trans-unit.source: An object that represents the OAEP encryption standard with a SHA512 hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto que representa o padrão de criptografia OAEP com um algoritmo de hash SHA512.

trans-unit.source: The first object to compare.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro objeto a ser comparado.

trans-unit.source: The second object to compare.
trans-unit.target: O segundo objeto a ser comparado.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether two specified <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> objects are equal.
trans-unit.target: Indica se dois objetos <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> especificados são iguais.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <see langword="left" /> and <see langword="right" /> are equal; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <see langword="left" /> e <see langword="right" /> forem iguais; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Two <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding> objects are equal if their <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode%2A> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.OaepHashAlgorithm%2A> property values are equal.
trans-unit.target: Dois <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding> objetos são iguais se seus <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode%2A> e <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.OaepHashAlgorithm%2A> valores de propriedade são iguais.

trans-unit.source: The first object to compare.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro objeto a ser comparado.

trans-unit.source: The second object to compare.
trans-unit.target: O segundo objeto a ser comparado.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether two specified <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> objects are unequal.
trans-unit.target: Indica se dois objetos <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> especificados são desiguais.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <see langword="left" /> and <see langword="right" /> are not equal; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <see langword="left" /> e <see langword="right" /> não forem iguais; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Two <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding> objects are not equal if their <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode%2A> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.OaepHashAlgorithm%2A> property values are not equal.
trans-unit.target: Dois <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding> objetos não são iguais se seus <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode%2A> e <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.OaepHashAlgorithm%2A> valores de propriedade não são iguais.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that represents the PKCS #1 encryption standard.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto que representa o padrão de criptografia PKCS #1.

trans-unit.source: An object that represents the PKCS #1 encryption standard.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto que representa o padrão de criptografia PKCS #1.

trans-unit.source: Returns the string representation of the current <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Retorna a representação de cadeia de caracteres da instância <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding" /> atual.

trans-unit.source: The string representation of the current object.
trans-unit.target: A representação de cadeia de caracteres do objeto atual.

trans-unit.source: The string representation of a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding> object is the concatenation of its <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode%2A> and `OaepHashAlgorithm.Name` properties.
trans-unit.target: A representação de cadeia de caracteres de um <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding> objeto é a concatenação de seus <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RSAEncryptionPadding.Mode%2A> e `OaepHashAlgorithm.Name` propriedades.
